<note n="1237002" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1237002">抵＝控ヵ【甲】</note>
<note n="1237003" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1237003">以下第九，十之二紙缺丁</note>
