<note n="1237006" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1237006">據＝諸ヵ【甲】</note>
<note n="1237007" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1237007">以下第十三，十四，十五，十六之四紙缺丁</note>
